{"tid":1837791,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"品蔥:  武漢疫情已是Mr. Shithole執政生涯最大的挑戰","createTime":"2020-01-23T18:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T18:52:54.000Z","uid":5195,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1a5349d62e9da55668063b0781c5ca467b483e12","tid":1837791,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:50:48.000Z","msg":"從修憲，到淨網封號，709律師抓捕，新疆集中營，貿易戰，香港問題，台灣問題，到如今的武漢病毒<br />\n每一次習近平都沒有做出適當的選擇，每一次都避開了正確的答案。<br />\n偉在習近平手中能打的牌越來越少，身邊報團的敵人越來越多，沒有他如何宣揚自己的&ldquo;偉大領袖&rdquo;的稱呼，蔓延國家後部遭受嚴峻的挑戰。<br />\n未來可預見這位老人的下場，被黨內盟友拋棄，被手下心腹背叛，被國民人民唾棄，被寫進歷史恥辱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pincong.rocks/article/12787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pincong.rocks%2Farticle%2F12787&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=d55a2b86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pincong.rocks/article/12787</a>"},{"pid":"3343302cb193652b8ddcbb8aeb2b37ee734e78f8","tid":1837791,"uid":131188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:52:54.000Z","msg":"侵侵: Am I a joke to you? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}